title: Spain Will Suspend Catalan Independence Push
description: Oct.19 -- Spain will proceed with the suspension of the Catalan government's powers following the refusal by Regional President Carles Puigdemont to drop his claim to independence. Bloomberg's Maria Tadeo reports on "Bloomberg Surveillance."
